# Free Gmail SMTP Configuration
#
# NOTE: If you receive authentication errors using your regular password:
# 1. Go to your Google Account > Security > 2-Step Verification and enable it.
# 2. Search for "App Passwords" or go to: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. Generate a new app password (e.g. name it "BN School ERP").
# 4. Copy the 16-character code and paste it in SMTP_PASS below (without spaces).

